1. ‘죽반과 매반의 수학성적은 차이가 없다’ 라는 가설을 검증하시오.


  • 참고 : data는 매,난,국,죽 4개의 반 학생들의 성적 데이터이다.
theme_set(theme_gray(base_family="AppleGothic"))
par(family = "AppleGothic")

# 1. 데이터 준비
head(data)
##   stuno cls gen kor eng math sci art group subTotal subMean
## 1 10101  매  남  55  84   50  40  59     B      189      63
## 2 10102  매  남  29  94   41  87  57     B      164      55
## 3 10103  매  여  28  80   68  41 100     A      176      59
## 4 10104  매  여  45  74   48  88  75     C      167      56
## 5 10105  매  여  28  69   57  91  66     B      154      51
## 6 10106  매  남  86  51   68  59  92     A      205      68
mjmath = data %>% filter(cls %in% c('죽', '매')) %>% select(cls, math)

mjmath$cls = factor(mjmath$cls, levels=c('죽','매'), labels=c('죽', '매'))

# 2. 데이터 확인 (기술통계 + 그래프)
describeBy(mjmath$math, mjmath$cls, mat = T)
##     item group1 vars   n     mean       sd median  trimmed     mad min max
## X11    1     죽    1 120 63.46667 23.49358   63.5 63.38542 31.8759  25 100
## X12    2     매    1 120 63.84167 23.15929   62.0 63.83333 31.1346  26 100
##     range       skew  kurtosis       se
## X11    75 0.02557417 -1.397709 2.144661
## X12    74 0.04867267 -1.371330 2.114145
orgpar = par(no.readonly = T)     
layout(matrix(c(1,1,2,3), 2, 2, byrow = T))
boxplot(mjmath$math ~ mjmath$cls)
hist(mjmath$math[mjmath$cls == '죽'])
hist(mjmath$math[mjmath$cls == '매'])

par(orgpar)

# 3. 등분산 검정
var.test(mjmath$math ~ mjmath$cls, data = mjmath) 
## 
##  F test to compare two variances
## 
## data:  mjmath$math by mjmath$cls
## F = 1.0291, num df = 119, denom df = 119, p-value = 0.876
## alternative hypothesis: true ratio of variances is not equal to 1
## 95 percent confidence interval:
##  0.7171975 1.4765803
## sample estimates:
## ratio of variances 
##           1.029077
# 4. t-test 수행
t.test(mjmath$math ~ mjmath$cls, data = mjmath,
       alternative = c("two.sided"),
       var.equal = T,                
       conf.level = 0.95)
## 
##  Two Sample t-test
## 
## data:  mjmath$math by mjmath$cls
## t = -0.12452, df = 238, p-value = 0.901
## alternative hypothesis: true difference in means is not equal to 0
## 95 percent confidence interval:
##  -6.307614  5.557614
## sample estimates:
## mean in group 죽 mean in group 매 
##         63.46667         63.84167
# 5. 결과 그래프 
mu1 = 63.46667
se1 = 2.144661
rn1 = sort(rnorm(1000, mu1, se1))

plot(rn1, dnorm(rn1, mu1, se1), col='green', type = 'l', main = '평균점수',
     xlim = c(50, 80), ylim = c(0, 0.25)) 
abline(v=mu1, col="green", lty=5)

mu2 = 63.84167
se2 = 2.114145
rn2 = sort(rnorm(1000, mu2, se2))

par(new = T) 

plot(rn2, dnorm(rn2, mu2, se2), col='red', type = 'l', main = '평균점수',
     xlim = c(50, 80), ylim = c(0, 0.25))
abline(v=mu2, col="red", lty=5)



2. 4개반 수학성적의 유사도(동질의 정도)를 분석하시오.


theme_set(theme_gray(base_family="AppleGothic"))
par(family = "AppleGothic")

# 기술 통계 확인
describeBy(data$math, data$cls, mat = T)
##     item group1 vars   n     mean       sd median  trimmed     mad min max
## X11    1     국    1 120 63.59167 22.13385   68.0 64.36458 25.9455  25 100
## X12    2     난    1 120 63.08333 22.22255   63.5 63.18750 29.6520  25 100
## X13    3     매    1 120 63.84167 23.15929   62.0 63.83333 31.1346  26 100
## X14    4     죽    1 120 63.46667 23.49358   63.5 63.38542 31.8759  25 100
##     range        skew  kurtosis       se
## X11    75 -0.33203681 -1.159495 2.020535
## X12    75 -0.08103377 -1.244699 2.028632
## X13    74  0.04867267 -1.371330 2.114145
## X14    75  0.02557417 -1.397709 2.144661
# 그래프로 데이터 확인하기 (ggplot2)
ggplot(data, aes(x=cls, y=kor)) +
  geom_boxplot(outlier.colour = 'blue') +
  ggtitle("각반 국어 성적")  # 반별 box

ggplot(data, aes(x=kor)) +
  geom_histogram(binwidth = 10, col="white") +
  facet_grid(. ~ data$cls)   # 반별 hist

# 등분산 검정 
bartlett.test(data$math ~ data$cls, data=data)
## 
##  Bartlett test of homogeneity of variances
## 
## data:  data$math by data$cls
## Bartlett's K-squared = 0.63086, df = 3, p-value = 0.8893
# ANOVA 분석
aaa = aov(data$math ~ data$cls, data = data)
summary(aaa)
##              Df Sum Sq Mean Sq F value Pr(>F)
## data$cls      3     36      12   0.023  0.995
## Residuals   476 246574     518
# Welch's ANOVA One-way test 
oneway.test(data$math ~ data$cls, data = data, var.equal = F)
## 
##  One-way analysis of means (not assuming equal variances)
## 
## data:  data$math and data$cls
## F = 0.023384, num df = 3.00, denom df = 264.37, p-value = 0.9951
# 사후 분석
TukeyHSD(aaa)
##   Tukey multiple comparisons of means
##     95% family-wise confidence level
## 
## Fit: aov(formula = data$math ~ data$cls, data = data)
## 
## $`data$cls`
##             diff       lwr      upr     p adj
## 난-국 -0.5083333 -8.083622 7.066956 0.9981582
## 매-국  0.2500000 -7.325289 7.825289 0.9997790
## 죽-국 -0.1250000 -7.700289 7.450289 0.9999723
## 매-난  0.7583333 -6.816956 8.333622 0.9939689
## 죽-난  0.3833333 -7.191956 7.958622 0.9992063
## 죽-매 -0.3750000 -7.950289 7.200289 0.9992568
# 6. 동질성 결과 그래프
plot(TukeyHSD(aaa))

# plot 함수 작성 (반복 제거)
draw = function(rn, mu, se, col){
  plot(rn, dnorm(rn, mu, se), col=col, type='l',
       xlim = c(50,80), ylim = c(0, 0.25))
  abline(v=mu, col=col, lty=5)
}
  
# 4개 한번에 그리기
mu = 63.59167; se = 2.020535; rn = sort(rnorm(1000, mu, se))
draw(rn, mu, se, 'red')     #국
par(new = T)
mu = 63.08333; se = 2.028632; rn = sort(rnorm(1000, mu, se))
draw(rn, mu, se, 'blue')    #난
par(new = T)
mu = 63.8416; se = 2.11414; rn = sort(rnorm(1000, mu, se))
draw(rn, mu, se, 'green')   #매
par(new = T)
mu = 63.46667; se = 2.144661; rn = sort(rnorm(1000, mu, se))
draw(rn, mu, se, 'black')   #죽
 
legend('topright',
       legend = c('국', '난', '매', '죽'),
       pch = 8,
       col =c('red', 'blue', 'green', 'black'),
       bg='white')
